{"ts":"2026-07-12T18:52:48.595Z","author":"maintainer-agent","op":"create","patch":[{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/id","value":"pm-96vo"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/title","value":"GH-526: aggregate --sum/--avg accept unknown field names and silently report 0"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/description","value":"GH-526 (2026-07-12, repro with --no-extensions on 2026.7.12): pm aggregate --group-by validates its argument against a known field list and fails fast, but --sum/--avg accept any string and silently emit sum:0 / omit avg with null_count==count as the only signal. A realistic typo (--sum estimated_minute) pastes a silently-wrong 0 into governance reports. Fix: validate --sum/--avg field names against the summable-numeric domain (built-ins + registered numeric custom fields) with the existing Invalid-argument-value error shape; if free-form custom fields must stay allowed, emit an explicit unknown_field marker/warning when the field resolves to zero known occurrences. Sibling contrast: pm-bvns shipped the aggregation feature itself (closed — do not touch). Same fail-fast-over-silent-success principle as the dep colon-shorthand fix (pm-zazb)."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/type","value":"Issue"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/status","value":"open"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/priority","value":2},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/tags","value":["agent-ux","aggregate","cli","gh-issue","validation"]},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/created_at","value":"2026-07-12T18:52:48.595Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-07-12T18:52:48.595Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/author","value":"maintainer-agent"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/estimated_minutes","value":90},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/acceptance_criteria","value":"Unknown --sum/--avg field names are rejected with the same 'Invalid argument value' error shape as --group-by, listing known numeric fields including registered numeric custom fields; valid built-in and custom numeric fields keep aggregating; spec covers the estimated_minute typo case producing a hard error instead of sum:0; docs/contracts updated if help text changes"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/parent","value":"pm-mpbb"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/risk","value":"medium"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/confidence","value":"high"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/dependencies","value":[{"id":"pm-bvns","kind":"related","created_at":"2026-07-12T18:52:48.595Z"}]}],"before_hash":"3cc22dff72be7b14824654a7a64ea62b04799939b2fee54c1b5f52ca60bf6df0","after_hash":"1184cc8ef379d7c55b6fe531354684b5ec97948b817f97611732fdd17011fa72","message":""}
